ACCEPTED_1.message: Ar fheabhas. Luchtóidh mé na hearraí ar do long.

ACCEPTED_3.message: Ceart go leor. Tá súil agam gur duine iontaofa thú.

ACCEPTED_PICKUP_1.message: Ceart go leor, deimhneoidh mé go bhfuil na hearraí réidh lena mbailiú.

ACCEPTED_PICKUP_2.message: Bíodh sé ina mhargadh! Inseoidh mé do mo chomhghleacaithe go bhfuil tú ar an mbealach.

ADTEXT_1.message: SEACHADADH LASTA. Lasta a sheachadadh chuig réaltchóras {system}.

ADTEXT_2.message: IOMPAR DE DHÍTH. Earraí a iompar go dtí réaltchóras {system}. Íocfar {cash}.

ADTEXT_EXPENSIVE_1.message: SEACHADADH. Lasta luachmhar chuig réaltchóras {system}. Íocfar píolóta a bhfuil taithí aige/aici {cash}.

ADTEXT_LOCAL_1.message: SEACHADADH ÁITIÚIL. Earraí a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

ADTEXT_LOCAL_2.message: IOMPAR DE DHÍTH. Lasta áitiúil a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

ADTEXT_LOCAL_3.message: SEACHADADH ÁITIÚIL. Earraí a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

ADTEXT_PICKUP_1.message: BAILIÚ LASTA. Long de dhíth le lasta a bhailiú ó réaltchóras {system}.

ADTEXT_PICKUP_LOCAL_1.message: AISTRIÚ. Long de dhíth le lasta a aistriú ó {starport}.

ADTEXT_WHOLESALER_1.message: SEIRBHÍS LASTA. Long ag teastáil uainn le lasta a sheachadadh chuig réaltchóras {system}.

AMOUNT.description: Shown in mission summary. The amount of cargo

CEASE_FIRE.message: Cease fire, cease fire! I'm on your side!

COULD_YOU_REPEAT_THE_ORIGINAL_REQUEST.message: An ndéanfá an t-iarratas céanna arís?

DENY_1.message: I'm sorry, but this cargo is too valuable for me to hand over to an inexperienced pilot.

DENY_2.message: Níor chuala mé riamh fútsa. Níl aithne agam ort agus níl muinín agam asat.

DENY_3.message: Mo leithscéal, ach tá mé ag lorg píolóta a bhfuil seantaithí aige sa ghnó seo.

DENY_4.message: Mo leithscéal, ach ní dóigh liom go bhfuil an mianach ceart ionat chun an jab seo a chur i gcrích.

DENY_5.message: Ná cuir mo chuid ama amú. Tá tú beagán glas fós.

DENY_6.message: Tar ar ais nuair a bheidh níos mó taithí agat.

DISTANCE.description: distance in space, between two locations

ESCORT_CHATTER_1.message: Hostile craft detected. Let us attack it together.

ESCORT_CHATTER_2.message: Great. This pirate will be my first kill.

ESCORT_CHATTER_4.message: Proceed to your destination. I'll cover you.

ESCORT_CHATTER_5.message: Teailí hó. Seo é mo chéad ghabháil den lá.

FAILUREMSG_1.message: Tá an-díomá orm go raibh an seachadadh chomh mall sin. Ní bhfaighidh tú cianóg rua.

FAILUREMSG_2.message: You are too late! What should I do with this now, it's worthless!

FAILUREMSG_3.message: Listen, we were clear about the deadline. You can forget about getting payed.

FAILUREMSG_4.message: From now on, I will reject all job requests from you.

FAILUREMSG_FLUFFY_1.message: Marbhfháisc ort! D'fhan tú rófhada leis an seachadadh seo. Tá mo chuid peataí clúmhacha go léir marbh leis an ocras!

GUNS_GUNS_GUNS.description: Military radio call to avoid friendly fire. It indicates that the cannon has been activated and should ensure that other friendly pilots do not maneuver into the path of harm.

HOWMUCH_SINGULAR_1.description: This string is only used for 1 metric tons (singular)

HOW_SOON_MUST_IT_BE_DELIVERED.message: Cé chomh luath agus is gá dom é a sheachadadh?

INTROTEXT_1.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name}. D'íocfainn {cash} as {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

INTROTEXT_2.description: {name} is the full name of a person
INTROTEXT_2.message: Dia dhuit! Ba mhaith le Córas Iompair {name} {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl. Íocfaimid {cash} as seachadadh slán sábháilte.

INTROTEXT_3.message: Bail ó Dhia ort. Is mise {name}, bunaitheoir {name} Teo. Tá mé ag lorg duine iontaofa chun {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}). Íocfaidh mé {cash} as an eitilt {dist} solasbhliain ar fad.

INTROTEXT_EXPENSIVE_1.message: Go mbeannaí Dia duit. Táimid ag lorg píolóta a bhfuil seantaithí aige chun lasta a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl. D'fhéadfadh sé a bheith contúirteach. Íocfaimid {cash} as.

INTROTEXT_FLUFFY_1.description: this is used for the delivery of Quibbles, which is a nod to Tribble (star trek ref. see wikipedia)
INTROTEXT_FLUFFY_1.message: Haló, is mise {name}. Tá lasta clúmhach {cargoname} agam le seachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl. Íocfaidh mé {cash} as an seachadadh seo.

INTROTEXT_INFRASTRUCTURE_1.message: Dia dhuit! Is mise {name}. Ba mhaith le rialtas {system} {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl. Íocfaimid {cash} as.

INTROTEXT_LOCAL_1.message: Deas bualadh leat. Is mise {name}, fostaí de chuid riarachán {starport}. D'íocfaimis {cash} le duine éigin a bheadh ábalta {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

INTROTEXT_LOCAL_2.message: Hóra a chara. Is mise {name} agus íocfaidh mé {cash} as lasta {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport}, achar an-ghearr ar fad.

INTROTEXT_LOCAL_3.message: Is mise {name} agus caithfidh mé {cargoname} a sheoladh chuig cliant ag {starport}. Íocfaidh mé {cash} as an seachadadh seo.

INTROTEXT_MINING_1.description: {name} is the full name of a person
INTROTEXT_MINING_1.message: Dia dhuit! Ba mhaith leis an gcomhlacht mianadóireachta {name} {cargoname} a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl, chun mianach nua a thógáil. Íocfaimid {cash} as.

INTROTEXT_PICKUP_1.message: How do you do? My name is {name}, and I need a ship that is able to fly to {starport} in the {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}) system, to pickup {cargoname} and return to {dom_starport} in the {dom_system} ({dom_sectorx}, {dom_sectory}, {dom_sectorz}) system for {cash}. The distance to {system} is {dist} ly.

INTROTEXT_PICKUP_2.message: How are you? I'm {name}. One of my clients wants to import {cargoname} from {starport} in the {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}) system, {dist} ly distant. He pays {cash} for this cargo run. Return here to {dom_starport} in the {dom_system} ({dom_sectorx}, {dom_sectory}, {dom_sectorz}) system to unload the cargo.

INTROTEXT_PICKUP_LOCAL_1.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name}. Íocfaidh mé {cash} le duine éigin as lasta {cargoname} a thabhairt ó {starport} go {dom_starport}.

INTROTEXT_PICKUP_LOCAL_2.message: Hello. My name is {name}. My employer is willing to hire you for {cash} to help us relocate our warehouse by moving {cargoname} from {starport} to our new domicile {dom_starport}.

INTROTEXT_WEDDING_1.message: Dia dhuit. Ar chuala tú riamh faoi shéasúr na mbainiseacha ag {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz})? Ba mhaith linn {cargoname} a sheoladh chuige, {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl. Íocfar {cash} as. Céard a déarfá?

INTROTEXT_WHOLESALER_1.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name} agus is mórdhíoltóir mé i réaltchóras {system}. D'íocfainn {cash} as seachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

INTROTEXT_WHOLESALER_2.message: Dia dhuit! Is mise {name} agus is fostaí de chuid Breosla Uí Scanaill, Teo. D'íocfaimis {cash} as turas go dtí {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

I_AM_ON_MY_WAY.message: Sensors show that you are taking damage. I'm on my way.

I_HAVE_DEBITED_YOUR_ACCOUNT.message: I've debited your account with the missing goods.

I_NEED_HELP.message: I'm taking damage. I need help.

PIRATE_GRIPES_1.message: Damn! You will pay for this!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_1.message: Seo é an seachadadh deireanach a bheidh agat!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_2.message: Tá tú ag obair do {client}? Tá do phort seinnte!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_3.message: Hé a mhic, tabhair uait na hearraí. Anois!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_4.message: Ní shroichfidh tú do cheann scríbe riamh, a mhic.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_5.message: Á, boc mór eile ar a bhealach go {location}.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_6.message: Looks like you're carrying more than you can handle. Let me help you with that.

QUIBBLES.description: custom cargo, also used in the NewsEventCommodity module, a nod to Star Trek's Tribble (check wikipedia)

RISK_1.message: Tá súil agam nach mbeidh aon trioblóid ann.

RISK_2.message: Ní bheidh ach mar is gnáth.

RISK_3.message: This is valuable cargo, you should keep your eyes open.

RISK_4.message: D'fhéadfadh sé a bheith contúirteach. Ba chóir duit deimhniú go bhfuil tú ullamh.

RISK_5.message: This might be very risky, you could run into some significant resistance.

RISK_6.message: Ní féidir a bheith cinnte go sroichfidh tú do cheann scríbe slán sábháilte.

RISK_ART_1.message: Tá ráchairt mhór ar na hearraí i measc bailitheoirí ealaíne.

RISK_EXPENSIVE_1.message: Rinneamar ár seacht ndícheall an seachadadh a choinneáil faoi rún. Ach ní féidir linn a bheith cinnte riamh.

RISK_EXPENSIVE_2.message: Dúirt na gardaí linn go bhfuil dream anaithnid foghlaithe ag imeacht thart sa réaltchóras seo.

RISK_GEMS_1.message: It is possible that an unscrupulous jewel trader wants to intercept the cargo.

RISK_WHOLESALER_1.message: Ná buair do cheann. Tá patról gardaí réidh i gcás trioblóide.

RISK_WHOLESALER_2.message: Maybe there's a risk. But the police have promised us to patrol the area.

RISK_WHOLESALER_3.message: The risk is high. But an escort is ready to guard you.

SUCCESSMSG_1.message: Thank you for the delivery. You have been paid.

SUCCESSMSG_2.message: Thanks for the timely delivery. The money was transferred.

SUCCESSMSG_3.message: Excellent, it was a pleasure to work with you. I have paid the bill.

SUCCESSMSG_4.message: Thanks! I will definitely recommend you. Money has been transferred.

SUCCESSMSG_FLUFFY_1.description: Said when receiving a shipment of Quibbles (see wikipedia Tribble)
SUCCESSMSG_FLUFFY_1.message: Oh dear, what to do with so many fluffy beings. Either way, money has been sent.

URGENCY_1.message: Níl aon deifir ann. Caithfear é a sheachadadh roimh {date}.

URGENCY_3.message: Mar gheall ar an sceideal docht, caithfear é a sheachadadh roimh {date}.

URGENCY_4.message: Tá deifir orainn, agus dá bharr sin caithfear é a sheachadadh roimh {date}.

URGENCY_5.message: It is essential that the goods have been delivered before {date}.

URGENCY_FLUFFY_1.message: Because of the reproduction rate of the little animals and the limited food in the container, the delivery must be completed until {date}.

URGENCY_RADIOACTIVE_1.message: Because of the half-life period of this isotope, delivery must be completed by {date}.

WE_HAVE_LOADED_UP_THE_CARGO_ON_YOUR_SHIP.message: We have loaded up the cargo on your ship.

WHAT_IS_THIS.message: What's this? Have you jettisoned my cargo? Are you crazy?

WHYSOMUCH_2.message: Glac leis nó ná glac is cuma liom.

WHYSOMUCH_4.message: The pay reflects our wish for the goods to be delivered on time and in one piece.

WHYSOMUCH_5.message: See it as a bonus for you to be discreet about this delivery.

WHYSOMUCH_6.message: Bhuel, bheimis lánsásta níos lú airgid a thabhairt duit.

WHYSOMUCH_CENTRIFUGES_1.message: Some {cargoname} were destroyed due to a software error and have to be replaced urgently.

WHYSOMUCH_CHEMICAL_1.message: The production in the chemical plant depends on these goods and must not be interrupted. Nothing must stop the machine.

WHYSOMUCH_EXPENSIVE_2.message: Toisc go bhfuil na hearraí seo sách costasach.

WHYSOMUCH_FLUFFY_1.message: {cargoname} is a fast seller this season. You should invest in {cargoname} shares if you want to make a lot of money.

WHYSOMUCH_INFRASTRUCTURE_1.message: These goods are crucial for a construction project.

WHYSOMUCH_MINING_1.message: These goods are essential for the construction of a new mine.

WHYSOMUCH_URGENT_1.message: Tá an píolóta is ansa liom tinn, agus níl mórán ama agam.

WHYSOMUCH_URGENT_2.message: If we do not meet the delivery date, the project will come to a standstill.

WHYSOMUCH_WEDDING_1.message: So far I could not find anyone to perform this transport. When the season is over, my merchandise is worthless.

WHY_SO_MUCH_MONEY.message: Cén fáth a bhfuil an méid sin airgid i gceist?

YOU_DO_NOT_HAVE_ENOUGH_CARGO_SPACE_ON_YO.message: Níl go leor spáis do lasta ar do long.

YOU_DO_NOT_HAVE_ENOUGH_EMPTY_CARGO_SPACE.message: Please come back when you have sufficient cargo space.
